thread.title: Anne Jackson

author: Anne Jackson
title: Anne Jackson
text: We were on our way to Europe with significant amount of luggage. We rented a car, which we thought was appropriate in size, but luckily we were given a brandnew Pajero, where all could fit in including children in a very comfortable way. The fuel economy was oustanding, so it balanced out the higher rate for renting this particular car.
